uot;再尾碼就出現到字選擇??</blockquote><br />\n可以入繁體出簡體字&lt;&lt;Google 粵語輸入法"},{"pid":"118176aa152ae770d38c77a95418984d0e306bae","tid":141171,"uid":88099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"用慣混合輸入法"},{"pid":"51043c0852ff8906cd66da9db095fc8ae5de36f1","tid":141171,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇邊款輸入法,<br />\n可以入繁體出簡體字<br />\n同埋倉頡mode時如果只記得速成點打, 就打頭碼加&quot;?&quot;再尾碼就出現到字選擇??</blockquote><br />\n百資輸入法做到以上既野，自己啱啱搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e15e9d41f42d5037745ed2cd530889b9761d62","tid":141171,"uid":42318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mixed keyboard</blockquote><br />\n我都係用呢個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312c34c471cb4119616db2716d72efa3ae049947","tid":141171,"uid":34880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"sony內置keyboard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e5613e0c6773e9300da8c44efad0b8ff012b8d","tid":141171,"uid":12820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Simplified Cangjie keyboard<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.milesleung.android.softKeyboard.simplifiedCangjieKeyboard&amp;hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.milesleung.android.softKeyboard.simplifiedCangjieKeyboard%26hl%3Dzh-TW&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=08aa746c\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.milesleung.android.softKeyboard.simplifiedCangjieKeyboard&amp;hl=zh-TW</a></blockq